'''Black Eight''' was a [[Type II Orbital Repair Yard]] assigned to the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] forces of [[Sixth Negative Regions|Black Sword Command]].

==History==
In [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]], it was based at the [[Yevetha]]n world of [[Wakiza]] in the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]]. Eight months after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], Imperial forces evacuated Wakiza's shipyards, during which Yevethan forces captured several vessels. The yards were afterwards taken over by the Yevetha and moved to a secure location.<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

